==Trivia==
*The King Black Dragon was given three heads upon his transition to [[RuneScape 2|''RuneScape 2'']]
*The [[King Black Dragon lair|King Black Dragon's lair]] is much smaller in RuneScape Classic than it is in RuneScape 2
